Description:
Annotation on the envelope: "Rubens Zeichnungen"

- First subfolder (Annotation: "Rubens-Zeichnung Bekehrung des Paulus") addressed (inside) to "Herrn Dr. Hans Gerhard Evers Heidelberg Bismarckstr. 17":
    - Draft text: "Eine Zeichnung zur "Bekehrung des Paulus" von Rubens" by Evers
    - Extracts from different publications
    - Notes of the seminary about 'Callisto' drawing (dated 1949)
- Reproductions of drawings
- List of Rubens' drawings
- Paper about Leonardo's studies of tree by E. Schalkhauβer
- Extracts from different publications about drawings
- Text: "Zwei Zeichnungen zur Antwerpener Kreuzaufrichtung"
- Second subfolder:
    - Photos of the essays 'Eine neuerworbene Skizze aus dem Rubens-Kreise' by W. v. Bode and 'Van Dycks Zeichnung 'Abladen der Jagdbeute' by L. Burchard in "Amtliche Berichte aus den preusz. Staatssammlungen" (1917 and 1919)
    - Photos of the essay 'Rubens ähnliche van - Dyck - Zeichnungen' by L. Burchard in "Berliner Kunstgeschichtliche Gesellschaft" 1932
    - Extracts from different publications
    - Photos of 'Rubens Drawings' by L. van Puyvelde in "Burlington Magazine" 77? 1941?
    - Photos of 'Rubens as a Draughtsman' by Regteren-Altena, in "Burlington Magazine"
    - Photos of drawings
    - Photos of 'Nyerhvervede Rubens tegninger' by J. Sthyr, in "Kunstmuseets Aarscrift" n.23, 1936
    - Photos of 'Zu Peter Paul Rubens als Zeichner' by F. Thöny, in "Berliner Amtl. Berichte" n.61, 1940
- Correspondence with the director of the Albertina (dated 1949), with Friedrich von Artus (dated 1944), with Julius Böhler (dated 1942), 
- Bibliographic references
- Article: 'Zeichnungen von Rubens. Austellung in Brüssel'
- Third subfolder (Annotation: "Rubens Zeichnungen: Landschaft"):
    - Photos of landscapes
    - Draft text: "Die Landschaftszeichnungen des P. P. Rubens"
    - Extracts from different publications
- Fourth subfolder (Annotation: "Bekehrung des Paulus"):
    - Reproductions of 'The Conversion of Saint Paul' and its sketch
    - Draft text: "Eine Zeichnung zur "Bekehrung des Paulus" von Rubens" by Evers
    - Correspondence with Gustav Grote (dated 1945), with Hannema, with Hofrat (dated 1943), with E. Trautscholdt (dated 1943), with Hans Boerner (dated 1943)
    - Photos of 'Die Bekehrung des Paulus bei Rubens' by E. Kieser, in "Cicerone XIX", 2, 1927
